metadata.name: Weed Porn: Runtz #001
metadata.description: Featured is the original Runtz strain, grown by Yung LB, cultivated in an undisclosed location in Michigan. Filmed vertically, in 4K RAW uncompressed, and lightly color graded for an honest look of this beautiful bud. Focus pulled manually with a 100mm macro lens. Content created by Trichome Media.
